{"tid":889263,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女性最想擁有的臉蛋 第一名果然是她！","createTime":"2018-11-04T12:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T00:51:34.000Z","uid":9573,"like":9,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4a75d7be2e85e2150d39371f418764edfaf77a96","tid":889263,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"30歲日本女星新垣結衣因演出《月薪嬌妻》人氣爆棚，更被網友暱稱為「我老婆」、「結衣老婆」，她的高人氣不僅迷到男性，就連女性都直喊想變成她！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/s6OI2viQJAV_ElCI2ROOxw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/490a9a2224f4dd7dd5ce820cfa3a8a05\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fs6OI2viQJAV_ElCI2ROOxw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F490a9a2224f4dd7dd5ce820cfa3a8a05&h=89d7761c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲新垣結衣因演出《月薪嬌妻》人氣爆棚，被網友暱稱為「我老婆」。<br />\n<br />\n新垣結衣去年睽違10年於「女性票選最想擁有的臉蛋」排行冠軍，今年她演出電影版《Gode Blue3空中急診英雄》及《非獸性男女》。日本「女性最想擁有的臉蛋」票選今（2）日結果出爐，朱千雪二連霸奪下冠軍。而今年的亞軍依然是演出《房仲女王》、《西鄉殿》、《指定律師》等戲劇的北景川子，季軍則是演出《法醫女王》、《高嶺之花》的石原聰美，第四名則是井川遙，第五名為深田恭子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.showwall.com/wp/tracy_chu/free/334417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.showwall.com%2Fwp%2Ftracy_chu%2Ffree%2F334417.jpg&h=0e42c0d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲朱千雪獲第12屆「女性票選最想擁有的臉蛋」排行冠軍。"},{"pid":"f8387494200558d320646ae346359072d4e1a590","tid":889263,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:24:05.000Z","msg":"北景川子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642c55f2acc29674eb7dc09f430deab68b336d14","tid":889263,"uid":49197,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:25:46.000Z","msg":"果然係結衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw你po隻大口怪未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a87b2f5a87b4cade230871c3b2e92abbcd0438e","tid":889263,"uid":157872,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:31:13.000Z","msg":"突登入黎睇千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533e8322c96286f3b80ac2a888e4cdaef12d90f1","tid":889263,"uid":145589,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:35:36.000Z","msg":"唔覺得新壺垣結衣靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46579498cbf93035a1c6746e7b9ecf330739dc12","tid":889263,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:38:34.000Z","msg":"老態出現了<br />\n個眼袋..."},{"pid":"4f66a0183f1f4f3d109f94ed7af7c53f309730d1","tid":889263,"uid":183601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"之前好似有隻支那雞扮佢, 仲要進軍日本"},{"pid":"4fc0a4cfb38d3e39582ea80b597fb8a7021076a1","tid":889263,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"533e8322c96286f3b80ac2a888e4cdaef12d90f1","tid":889263,"uid":145589,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:35:36.000Z","msg":"唔覺得新壺垣結衣靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:42:03.000Z","msg":"講靚，初出道嘅堀北真希就真係眼前一亮啦"},{"pid":"9d861fa62d6e188216bf9810899e83b0b3120661","tid":889263,"uid":168978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"both g"},{"pid":"04cfd3de16bce42005424d78baea1b2a3e690eec","tid":889263,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T14:26:51.000Z","msg":"點解仲未有人講 那個了唷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02e20e63bd0c0